title: Rapper Bun B Has Perfect Twin Names for Beyonce and Jay Z
text:
EXCLUSIVE
Rap legend Bun B 's got Beyonce and Jay Z covered with baby names for their new twins ... and it's exactly what the world needs right now.
We caught up with Bun B at a Habitat for Humanity event in Houston where he wasted no time dishing baby names for his famous pals.
Check it out ... he goes in one direction -- quite literally -- before coming up with some delightful names.
